genresAdvancedInfo.name: horror punk brasileiro
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Horror punk brasileiro is a subgenre of horror punk that originated in Brazil. It features many of the same elements as traditional horror punk, but often incorporates Brazilian cultural and musical influences. The music is typically fast and energetic, with lyrics that explore themes of horror, death, and the supernatural.
